<plot>Renè, a Neapolitan growing up in Milan, leads a gang of three who hang out after school, smoke pot, disco, and engage in muggings and petty theft. Their fence is the cynical and menacing Marcione. Renè invites a new kid, the rich and well-tailored Giorgio, to join the group over Marco's objections. Giorgio ratchets up the violence of their crimes, threatening sexual assault of a woman they rob and bashing the head of a pensioner. Renè's losing control: during two fateful days, Marco breaks with Renè and woos away Renè's girlfriend; Giorgio and Renè win a bet with Marcione; they are arrested for assault and car theft; and, upon release, take a further step into violence and oblivion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?451153</url></doc>
